---
import { Icon } from "@iconify/react"
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 transition-colors duration-300">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
        Sobre <span class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">Mí</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Desarrollador frontend apasionado por crear experiencias digitales excepcionales
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none text-center">
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-lg mb-6">
          Soy <strong class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">Eugenio Gordillo</strong>, 
          un desarrollador frontend especializado en crear aplicaciones web y móviles modernas. 
          Con más de <strong>3 años de experiencia</strong>, me apasiona transformar ideas 
          complejas en interfaces intuitivas y funcionales.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-lg mb-6">
          Mi enfoque se centra en el desarrollo de soluciones escalables utilizando las 
          tecnologías más actuales del ecosistema JavaScript. He trabajado en proyectos 
          que van desde <strong>aplicaciones empresariales</strong> hasta 
          <strong>plataformas móviles híbridas</strong>, siempre priorizando la 
          experiencia del usuario y la calidad del código.
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-lg">
          Me especializo en <strong>React</strong>, <strong>Angular</strong> y 
          <strong>Flutter</strong>, y tengo experiencia sólida en tecnologías de backend 
          como Node.js y bases de datos. Mi objetivo es seguir creciendo profesionalmente 
          mientras contribuyo al éxito de equipos de desarrollo innovadores.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-16">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-12 text-center">Stack Tecnológico</h3>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
          
        <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4 text-center">Frontend & Móvil</h4>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-3 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors shadow-sm">
              <Icon icon="skill-icons:javascript" width="32" height="32" client:load />
              <span class="text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-2">JavaScript</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-3 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors shadow-sm">
              <Icon icon="skill-icons:typescript" width="32" height="32" client:load />
              <span class="text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-2">TypeScript</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-3 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors shadow-sm">
              <Icon icon="skill-icons:react-dark" width="32" height="32" client:load />
              <span class="text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-2">React</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-3 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors shadow-sm">
              <Icon icon="skill-icons:nextjs-dark" width="32" height="32" client:load />
              <span class="text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-2">Next.js</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-3 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors shadow-sm">
              <Icon icon="skill-icons:angular-dark" width="32" height="32" client:load />
              <span class="text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-2">Angular</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-3 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors shadow-sm">
              <Icon icon="skill-icons:flutter-dark" width="32" height="32" client:load />
              <span class="text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-2">Flutter</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-3 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors shadow-sm">
              <Icon icon="skill-icons:tailwindcss-dark" width="32" height="32" client:load />
              <span class="text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-2">Tailwind</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-3 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors shadow-sm">
              <Icon icon="skill-icons:bootstrap" width="32" height="32" client:load />
              <span class="text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-2">Bootstrap</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-3 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors shadow-sm">
              <Icon icon="skill-icons:dart-dark" width="32" height="32" client:load />
              <span class="text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-2">Dart</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-3 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors shadow-sm">
              <Icon icon="skill-icons:kotlin-dark" width="32" height="32" client:load />
              <span class="text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-2">Kotlin</span>
            </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4 text-center">Backend</h4>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-3 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors shadow-sm">
              <Icon icon="skill-icons:nodejs-dark" width="32" height="32" client:load />
              <span class="text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-2">Node.js</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-3 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors shadow-sm">
              <Icon icon="skill-icons:expressjs-dark" width="32" height="32" client:load />
              <span class="text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-2">Express.js</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-3 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors shadow-sm">
              <Icon icon="skill-icons:php-dark" width="32" height="32" client:load />
              <span class="text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-2">PHP</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-3 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors shadow-sm">
              <Icon icon="skill-icons:laravel-dark" width="32" height="32" client:load />
              <span class="text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-2">Laravel</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-3 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors shadow-sm col-span-2">
              <Icon icon="skill-icons:python-dark" width="32" height="32" client:load />
              <span class="text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-2">Python</span>
            </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4 text-center">Bases de Datos</h4>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-3 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors shadow-sm">
              <Icon icon="skill-icons:mysql-dark" width="32" height="32" client:load />
              <span class="text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-2">MySQL</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-3 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors shadow-sm">
              <Icon icon="skill-icons:mongodb" width="32" height="32" client:load />
              <span class="text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-2">MongoDB</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-3 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors shadow-sm">
              <Icon icon="skill-icons:sqlite" width="32" height="32" client:load />
              <span class="text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-2">SQLite</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-3 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors shadow-sm">
          
              <Icon icon="devicon:firebase" width="32" height="32" client:load />
              <span class="text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-2">Firebase</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-3 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors shadow-sm col-span-2">
              <Icon icon="devicon:mysql" width="32" height="32" client:load />
              <span class="text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-2">SQL Server</span>
            </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4 text-center">Herramientas & DevOps</h4>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-3 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors shadow-sm">
              <Icon icon="skill-icons:docker" width="32" height="32" client:load />
              <span class="text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-2">Docker</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-3 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors shadow-sm">
              <Icon icon="skill-icons:aws-dark" width="32" height="32" client:load />
              <span class="text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-2">AWS</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-3 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors shadow-sm">
              <Icon icon="skill-icons:githubactions-dark" width="32" height="32" client:load />
              <span class="text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-2">GitHub Actions</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-3 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors shadow-sm">
              <Icon icon="logos:rabbitmq-icon" width="32" height="32" client:load />
              <span class="text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-2">RabbitMQ</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-3 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors shadow-sm col-span-2">
              <Icon icon="skill-icons:figma-dark" width="32" height="32" client:load />
              <span class="text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-2">Figma</span>
            </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 p-4">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-8 text-center">Habilidades Clave</h3>
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 rounded-lg bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
            <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-blue-600 dark:bg-blue-400 rounded-full flex-shrink-0"></div>
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Trabajo en equipo</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 rounded-lg bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
            <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-blue-600 dark:bg-blue-400 rounded-full flex-shrink-0"></div>
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Resolución de problemas</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 rounded-lg bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
            <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-blue-600 dark:bg-blue-400 rounded-full flex-shrink-0"></div>
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Adaptabilidad</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 rounded-lg bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
            <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-blue-600 dark:bg-blue-400 rounded-full flex-shrink-0"></div>
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Aprendizaje continuo</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 rounded-lg bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
            <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-blue-600 dark:bg-blue-400 rounded-full flex-shrink-0"></div>
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Comunicación efectiva</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 rounded-lg bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
            <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-blue-600 dark:bg-blue-400 rounded-full flex-shrink-0"></div>
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Gestión del tiempo</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 